### Health check
http://localhost:8080/health

### Test Ingestion
### My son Anish is going to college in Long Beach state college and he is working hard this year
### who is working hard?
### "why is Anish working hard?"
### who is studying and working hard?

POST http://localhost:8080/api/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "docId": "test-doc",
    "content": "Anish is studying at Long Beach State College. He is working hard. He also plays guitar. He is preparing for dental school. He enjoys biology and science."
}

### Ask question
POST http://localhost:8080/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the possible causes of p99 spikes?"
}

### Ingest PDF
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ingest-pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="docId"

test-pdf-doc
--WebAppBoundary--


###
POST http://localhost:8080/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "test-pdf-doc",
  "question": "What are the possible causes of p99 spikes?",
  "topK": 5
}

###
### Ingest JVM Flags PDF
